# step-verify — Deep Gap Analysis & Iterative Completion

**Purpose:** Comprehensive verification of SSS workflow steps (0-12, including conditional Steps 1.5 and 11b) with 100-point scoring.

## Command Usage

```bash
@step-verify --step=1              # Verify Step 1 only
@step-verify --step=0-12           # Verify all steps
@step-verify --step=1 --fix        # Verify and fix gaps
```

## Scoring System (100 Points Total)

| Category | Weight | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| Required Files | 20 | Core files exist |
| Required Sections | 30 | All sections present |
| Content Quality | 30 | Word count, tables, patterns |
| Checkpoints | 10 | HITL approval evidence |
| Success Criteria | 10 | Step-specific requirements |

## Verification Process

1. **Parse step parameter** - Support single step, range, or comma-separated list
2. **Load step definition** - Get required files, sections, patterns
3. **Execute checks** - Verify each criterion
4. **Calculate score** - Sum points from all categories
5. **Report gaps** - Show what's missing with fixes
6. **Auto-fix loop** (if --fix) - Iterate until 100% or max 5 iterations

## Score Thresholds

| Score | Status | Action |
|-------|--------|--------|
| 95-100 | ✅ Excellent | Ready for production |
| 80-94 | 🟡 Good | Minor gaps, review recommended |
| 60-79 | 🟠 Needs Work | Run --fix to address gaps |
| <60 | 🔴 Incomplete | Re-run the step command |
